<span id="freeTextContainer17878096603782356110">4.25 stars <br/>So this book is the last book in the Belle Meade series, I liked this one the best, Alxandra and Sy are really dynamic and I liked their interaction very much .. I liked how both of them achieved their dreams without sacrificing each other and both of them won in the end <br/>one thing I didn&apos;t like was how open ended the book was, so many things I wanted resolved but they didn&apos;t and this is the last book .. so I guess we will never know, but this was an enjoyable series overall </span>
  <span id="freeText17878096603782356110" style="display:none">4.25 stars <br />So this book is the last book in the Belle Meade series, I liked this one the best, Alxandra and Sy are really dynamic and I liked their interaction very much .. I liked how both of them achieved their dreams without sacrificing each other and both of them won in the end <br />one thing I didn't like was how open ended the book was, so many things I wanted resolved but they didn't and this is the last book .. so I guess we will never know, but this was an enjoyable series overall </span>
